         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[recto] For children; burnt copper, 4 drachmas [i.e. 96 gr]; calamine, 6 or 8 drachmas; opium, 2 or 4 drachmas; myrrh, 2 1/3 drachmas; erica, 2 drachmas; acacia, 6 drachmas; gum, 6 drachmas; use water until it becomes sufficiently glutinous in thickness. [verso] Station at Fla-: my pepper, 2 drachmas [i.e. 48 g]; litharge, 2 drachmas; myrrh, 4 drachmas; fat, 2 drachmas; gum, 10 drachmas; use wine . . .  gum and ingredients.</ab>
